Hagāri ma ʔat ʕoṣā ʕaḳšāyw
ʔat tihyī ha qaṭār
ma higīaʕ
ha rakēvet higīʕa
ma naʕaṣē ʕaḳšāyw ʔaxrēy_še higāʕnu
lehitraʔōt
šalōm leʔān ʔat holēḳet
ʔat holēḳet la bubā
ʔēyfo ha bubā gāra
ha bubā gāra be ʕeyn_xarōd
ʔeyḳ qorʔīm la bubā še gāra be ʕeyn_xarōd
ʔat nosāʕat levaqēr ʔet sābaʔ Sōrki
we mi ʕod
ʔēyzo sāvtaʔ
sāvtaʔ Sōrki
ʔanī loʔ xošēvet še ʔat mekirā ʔet sāvtaʔ Sōrki
ʔat loqāxat ʔitāḳ bgadīm ba tiq
ṣāma xulcā betōḳ ha tiq šel ʔābaʔ še hiʔ soxēvet ʕal ha katēf we ha ʔaqordiyōn ʕal ha šniyā we Hagāri halḳā ʕaḳšāyw me ha xēder
Hagāri ʔulāy taxzerī
šalōm
